:'''Wen Tianweng:''' Well if it isn't the kid from last time! At least you have enough conscience to come hang out with this old fart.
:'''Wen Tianweng:''' It's nothing important. Just that lately I've had to go fix those blockages every day. I can't move my old bones anymore.
:'''Wen Tianweng:''' Last time, when I was fixing my motorcycle, I almost knocked down the wall of the maintenance room, like Hosea Lazaro did.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052101_11-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052101_11-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wow, that's so cool.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052106-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Pff, that's nothing. Next time I should take you to see the galaxy-class Rose Roydz I hid in the corner of the railway platform. Now that's an eye-opener!
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' But that's all for later. Now, if you can find me 3 Ultra Nickel Parts, I'll treat you to as many Kapo-Kali as you want!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It doesn't sound like you can't move at all...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052109-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Really, I am not lying to you. Ouch, I hurt all over...
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' My tongue, teeth, and my mouth hurt. I can't keep talking nonsense with you, kid.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Now hurry, find me 3 Ultra Nickel Parts. In return, you can have all the Kapo-Kali you want!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} So you want to order me around.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052113-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Hey, how is that ordering you around? Young people should eat more and work more, that's how you stay healthy and out of trouble.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Not to mention, you just have to find 3 Ultra Nickel Parts for me and you can have all the Kapo-Kali you want!
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_300052115-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052115-->
:'''Wen Tianweng:''' You have no idea, the kind of things folks are willing to do just for a sip of that... elixir from heaven!
:'''Wen Tianweng:''' Go, go, enough chit-chatting. I'll be waiting!
:<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
