:{{DIcon|Talk}} Are there any gossips from the old days?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500217304-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Oh, I am best qualified to talk about this.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' You know Bernard, don't you? The stubborn old guy from the Department of Cosmic Geography who doesn't look very approachable. His eyebrows are fiercer than his eyes.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Don't be fooled by his seeming determination to prevent his apprentice from dating. You never could've guessed that he used to be quite the womanizer back in his younger days.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Back when he was young, Bernard fell in love for the first time with a girl from the Department of Insight. As his brothers, we all helped him to pursue her for a while.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Young love is always full of passion. I guess Bernard just saw his younger self in Rocky, haha.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' What's that? You want to know what happened then? Kiddo, I can't spill all the beans in one go. Stay tuned!
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Any unforgettable stories?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500217311-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' At my age, everything is unforgettable. You know what I mean?
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' I know young people these days hate to hear this, but nothing is truly unforgettable, and there's nothing you can't get over! If there is, it's only because you've been too lost to figure it out!
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Now that you brought it up, I am actually confused. I just remembered so many things all at once. The past really doesn't bear being remembered.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' How energetic Gunn used to be... And how strong Bernard was when he first joined us...
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' *sigh* How things have changed!
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What have you been working on lately?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500217317-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' I'm retired, so that might not be an accurate question. We normally just say what we've been playing with.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' I never got a proper education. I wouldn't understand Fool's Play like Gunn does. My life's work has been all about repairing and handling machines and vehicles, and now that I'm old, that's still the only thing I do.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Here, check this out. Don't think this is some child's plaything! The armored car this miniature model is based on has traveled on more roads than I could count! This model even has a perfect replica of the real thing's mechanized track.
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' I fixed this thing three times. Three times I managed to bring it back from the brink of death ...
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' Well, I think I'm done talking. These stories are all water under the bridge.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} No other questions.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500217324-->
::'''Wen Tianweng:''' It was fun chatting with you. I liked it! Come here again when you have time, kiddo. I might not have much in my possession, but I sure have more than enough stories to share.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Wen Tianweng:''' Kiddo, we meet again. Take a seat.
